Package: MetabolismExplorer
Title: Exploring Metabolism Patterns Based on Transcriptomic Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Jiajun", "Li", email = "11697636896@qq.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides tools to analyze and visualize metabolic pathway activities
    based on bulk or single-cell transcriptomic data, integrating differential expression,
    enrichment analysis, and pathway-based scoring approaches.
